式后数小时内启动&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=82ee7bd0468f47509e3dd7c3f6323fe1&amp;amp;_e=krdzJ4SE8a0X3Y7UBiYioLh5w6eufltGxXvZa1ZKqhuI9ac3G9syn7JF6M4VcUp1LLmCBIfkpPJlsZlfy9NREO_-0RacGLS_zqvEQqyzpWYmIskvVcILKWjcyoMu9Kpt5j0UgRqJj3-up9foE5Ujm3QwGNfKeqhjaocjOc4zNnuyuKAVyopHQ_R6gT64SC0gx2mcCb2wQVaqheDhvgNe1xFT2lvpmNr9R0K9m-P54uMraZtRVdfK_dmEvlb-x7JuAKdPtBCLCDma28EUHmtQL8_V-DAHcoO0oUqEYPto7h7FuEQA1YJhNXQLSo1nJgGxD1dz7n4G442GxpKjc6un7H0RZV3-CwAr6UglOi8a_ajDXcGyKIXjhdVbN0SBs2CZEXiMwzMMzSkGe5ntIyrXevgD3CGNZYj5_TzJdPDRRtMCOXBoTPYmBYkN3N1JJE3qPLgTDGihfQTXpF1qB-EVj4yrAO4goRlD3mAC9h_oXQkAOKKYI_q58xAvk_CbdxdwwLSHuT5RnMkz1O5127n1t27bev8EkeV9cPviTd5ukODn1RnBioxQg23ki8aqKsFSxWVT13RE5sTmwlKzru4PtBYvHkMW6a-nhh8upeIhfU1l7vKFp8R1YLD23JQM-OKV9ptzsIN3kE20gXDRLFGRz7PZSG_VHuX0JkZ7Czko9sTuPhwlm_ltnld7Asam5SQdWXAX-TiuX--xbQhtmuHCSKEdb1V4ZVjvng-jhdbxK7TpieMMpSktWzIfy00wqV6p3qjngKyJxclKbwTLHuoHLLTC_g38Lb13vQHjcdHv4_mxssoOwXFaxZe7yu99tvWqXrnWmuhnVYJr1IgeJN0pmw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;国家能源紧急状态&lt;/a&gt;。我们今天的时事通讯着眼于所有这些对绿色转型意味着什么。我们还将研究二十年的数据，寻找总统对美国长期排放趋势有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=82ee7bd0468f47509e3dd7c3f6323fe1&amp;amp;_e=krdzJ4SE8a0X3Y7UBiYioLh5w6eufltGxXvZa1ZKqhuI9ac3G9syn7JF6M4VcUp1st13HQkN_dIeFtwjGsmOgDxgf_VDCKn4wLjLfdNMdLe9Xn1iMRikcYiriEltD4TIef9kPQfQ0V-jRSUA8ZZx3_ErY6vGLm5ZZGZeFJlQqrODCKTirY5YIbtB_LGgFPAz9lGZCgvxKjA-iWPf05lvaOzdx9PZ-4RSMwIq8y04nvyUBtUERXvek24iIVSkvs4tFpEZ-mtP7kVbA9C-0iIMcw-vT6A7-FM69ho0wWCqMJFJQVTU9N7cOpancj4YDGk2dKsyE2G9GZLhcgZ45rSMRkhPkiF7krDCjwMGvpV0ZePGEkdfktkQ7aTCP7ulsy-ZElAGuKMHvKPiFNp0zPHKYYDN8vHRIwzS8lwX09hV4KlFObyzp8gei7KIKpL9PSK5r0dwlkbHshz9c_DYLeeGWm42PcxoX9alSH-a8vMoinmBk6G-sLk0Y-mUjW7uoxaRYuQjtCgbjQTpJXWFX1EQPHy8v3jt4D-Oz0ntTyixc8DkhxQ71Jza4YYvmnmbrTLCNkRYqv8D-6G6T5SeEedXQBewgGfg9MU5XynVRdVgwwJDAdOl0zyQkCX1KR15rGTsXHfbByIyHBPwQGOqc89qRgsCXERFWwQtCgaUB6HYsmvyTN2r0q4Hq74Df3OeZ1rs0MGZotGdxB5o6DDzR6RfEE_F95nZmSXPl2UPQ5zE