ong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;，召集了 2,600 多名律师和近 2,200 名领事馆工作人员，为居住在美国的约 500 万无证墨西哥人提供支持，这些人面临特朗普的威胁，将实施该国历史上“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=f0e6a8b8f64d49d98ae6f177b02fb550&amp;amp;_e=aXq9WtOaKSso0FM-oIlNY1-xbTVhEicbt7XhBgNIfOVZvqGVHOjlFqWUc-Ao8mnksyUIvF3Pw-BaIqmR1Ia2OfoWMq1Ee8Z_rxWOR7n3ZjBuuqw_UI7lcgzZNJdMeGtI4QZgo4NkOK3RKd3ZJBvJ3egNphB3Ixw72Rx1x9SqhegKICipbpXWt30n-Ou1t26zoU6WOrlkHhQs2hVBv-jdfJeyig7dLRxiS0E5Mb__tvl4hLx7Ctmu420PBlj-mdgaRkxi6Wace5Fz4o14fRy8_UEu23Ybn5DxjRWFsyMPjjn34m9i7iBCcjxpcdBLcp5H9nfm7ESKZobf7RjDxUU1HQBzekoWjlcSXvELQf1rnN-fXRE2zKIMA10GpknN6HBqRLH9JzYH_nP_M3255i98oM8FdJuaUzh8uvfD7XlrTY84fqblLCTKSeE8vpC3avrX6vUB9noQXA6oPFPwYXQH79qZHMKbHsUsfAqXno3pDTkboF50QlRbd4v00aBfIEFJCsZ07CDEqzMbi5AJ334P--OjrdTRbGI5zOp0uGqVzl72ZOLlI4Oj5WLVpn_g-EesiOFAhB5DzmDRnWZbvOyKNuwQUGYV2r1TYE1GEfrSbLaytpbZ8yj8GtBYSXNRVtu7zoPVGGrR9MUGpuZRFb48x5-y58irKNjiYStk3YPGU7PXtX2BAgsN_MzdBltDRqcOh7EnmcxHYIZcrGRIhGNh9UBihCngj6jZ6wu2a2zy05lStbU5PJ30wXIxU2JNzT6vuduKjAuqRZwMOcgbc4KQUwsrAZ_-X0AWuiKgHZjuBPXh-fftX6-3way7HoDLXIjJnzsTOCP67M4JZlmLr5Jjbg%3D%3D"&gt;最大规模的驱逐&lt;/a&gt;行动”。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;德国绿党在下个月提前大选中的主要候选人&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;周末前往极度保守的巴伐利亚州进行竞选宣传，此举是&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=f0e6a8b8f64d49d98ae6f177b02fb550&amp;amp;_e=aXq9WtOaKSso0FM-oIlNY1-xbTVhEicbt7XhBgNIfOVZvqGVHOjlFqWUc-Ao8mnkwxOiAGDquVVyMfYuAHBxWUJTUCvTxjU5mAMVq5EszY_y84P3hAlQzrDSgCX_wM5b7-x_38U-ygV3yFOiNAmzkTEsYCqO2NZvNvdo4SlI48d--CP1lyvV26dhcaCR7aIFriKYI4MA9MjATvjiHS8x9CL2d34s196XcbHREL8X35u06-CPOD8kEuc84hEJZ93Y_GXbtm9xZtvW-DPq4vGm_rlz98IRGtv-prWhcAtm1nK2JjjsIOQQEmYyqMh3Q4hoAJb2ou4d_1ZmIL1gcFGrLRnxM-8w-RK5-3OC9-xH2mAL6-lFYcU0lw0UzADFvrFKlBfrgD9eN_2ZVCOHnDcocnk-WCv-KQUreA3Y3xVwQTyAijeljLUL0Ne1mo