ing-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;孤立主义的代价：&lt;/strong&gt;一位读者写道，“全世界的恐惧和仇恨”正在助长世界各地的孤立主义。而“资本市场却忽视了反全球化的巨大代价。” （ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbe0bd659d894c958b24044e1ae467ba&amp;amp;_e=vmU5GxOGhYA0OGjPUrAy3vtug7IDPN2nwEJh-pBzigKFrFJXAaeDfJrpfbjuklCnE1c8L1Z2frtHbFYeE513ZR93f2RGOJXV4FtFjwZyPtCrWBtIbJgRhOpfEPnt0fobWlk5BC6dH_jMJGVILpyvgbEw9t_NdjZN-xIrnkeOLlL40QD49k02j_38itcDojki1_t9pAqxXcQKrtyuN7KzOw4hMcV1guvDZCt5aPGRjJFz6TKJ983dF8CIPbbIt0-6Dr_cV8r_nNsC5KBjv8ZS9c-o0c_PkRGQPnRbox0sytn7EbjWejZsk9zZGBq3ROVw4vUFis36PaJqN0yxetD21x3xr2DuTKPMmtZftWvJ9wJau0QiZ4L5KOHimwixw322vRTzqG2RCL3yUZkV0FmJGULOceRCvP_dTMqaqDIzwQ9viN90Y60s2nCYLGann3tWY4HO1rTvrmCoUNXtSnEOgw1TA0E2ZO3YEN1krrFtNwY1bMWh62F2mIe5uIWpm_uvujYDT9U6qXrWZolXk0y7pq6txEegVu9XdOLF9Ax6PlsOXl9oakuvA6EBtryLOTXuzg_mmKc-EK7NO5h2uJ_UiURmBRK8T-xp5FiwhNfxmTBpc0wHzszp_ytj8spkwwWgzbg0bsGOdLvZrUILv63WT_RSdXl-y8cm0YpdueDBRGC4dPTarkvlTcfsjkKoA9wGodP5O_5hsntE-IjBp2NTsOKN3C1n_cjunmx3CGetxjS36mouqYPa67mylJttghpMkGB9haSPGyrVwiV__BhOhv0uHDUn63saV8U4ee4g2bKTrFddwp0my10SgAjio_FR" target="_blank" title="令人惊讶的是，市场似乎并未受到地缘政治的影响"&gt;我们在 11 月的采访中探讨了这个主题&lt;/a&gt;。）&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;随着孤立主义的持续，出国旅行的愿望会减少吗？&lt;/strong&gt; （我们建议您查看 Bloomberg Pursuits 的《 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbe0bd659d894c958b24044e1ae467ba&amp;amp;_e=vmU5GxOGhYA0OGjPUrAy3vtug7IDPN2nwEJh-pBzigJno8bvmmBm9fq0MRN3cXGin5wdzdY0ChpGlFCN53OTDqvC0CrUOhyqht9u2IBept07dSfE-8QPOtfXc_X6mPu_4Z62r_f5Fq8sQvQ4t6dUP_pY21toTg1f5vTOP9HRGYTVHfinJrKoPdR9SmpJLr6Nu9Zv5fO4nnFsnfvK2uRxn-iFjodIXnIy1RoxO7-VnRv802FRwL2cPUAN-Q-mV2EmJ-5R8fiaPpKiSf4eZuTkfZSsxiy1V62umCsJV2PHHfVJcJ_CGsMdj-ojVhkQDRcAWYCvAEW4IsDn5kyk6qpsolZqZzqTOHmw6dhdSju3OyO8e30BPXNY